+#### LOW — No end-to-end test for 4h bar count per session day
+
+**File:** `tests/test_intraday.py`
+
+**Issue:**
+The test suite validates `_align_session` and `_resample_1h_to_4h` in isolation but there is no test that exercises the full `_fetch_yfinance` pipeline (or a mock equivalent) and asserts the expected number of 4h bars per day. The partial candle problem identified above would not be caught by the existing tests.
