+**Minimal fix:**
+Add a test that feeds 6 synthetic 1h session bars (10:00–15:00 ET, EDT timezone) into `_resample_1h_to_4h` and asserts exactly how many 4h bars are returned and whether each has 4 constituent bars — making the partial-candle behaviour explicit and testable regardless of what the threshold policy becomes.
