+| DST handling (spring-forward) | **CORRECT** — pytz `tz_convert` is DST-aware; test covers EDT |
+| 4h OHLCV aggregation (open=first, high=max, low=min, close=last, volume=sum) | **CORRECT** |
+| Partial 4h windows with < 2 source bars are dropped | **CORRECT** — `counts >= _MIN_BARS_PER_4H_CANDLE` |
+
