+- [P2] MEDIUM: Restore the requirements package entry — /Users/josephwong/TradingAgents/requirements.txt:1-1
+  This removes the `.` entry from `requirements.txt`, so workflows that install with `pip install -r requirements.txt` no longer install the package or console script. Minimal fix: restore `.` in the file, consistent with the handoff note that `requirements.txt` should still contain it.
